<div id="what-is-passenger">
  <h1 class="solo-h1">What is Passenger?</h1>
  <p>Phusion Passenger is an <label>open source</label> <b>web application server</b>.
  It handles HTTP requests, manages processes and resources, and enables administration,
  monitoring and problem diagnosis.</p>

