  <p class="video-sub-text">Phusion Passenger - the smart app server</p>
  <p>Passenger is very easy to use, makes deploying in production much easier and is scalable. If you aren't already familiar with the benefits, you can <a href="https://www.phusionpassenger.com/advantages">learn more about them</a>.</p>

  <p>Passenger supports multiple programming languages, of which <%= render_partial("/shared/lang") %> is one.
  Passenger can also serve multiple applications at the same time (it is multitenant).</p>

